title: Nuclear ANXIETY! with Joe List | Chris Distefano Presents: Chrissy Chaos | EP 65
description:
WELCOME to Chrissy Chaos! 
 
Chrissy CHAOS is joined by comedian Joe List! You know him from his podcast @Tuesdays with Stories and his comedy special Are You Mad At Me?
Joe just recently closed his Netflix account, but will open it again for Chris' comedy special, Speshy Weshy, and John Wayne Gacy documentary. Chris's new favorite show, Conversations with a Killer: John Wayne Gacy Tapes where he explains his handcuff tricks, what a psycho clown!
Joe and Chris remember the last time working together was on The Impractical Jokers Cruise, in February of 2020, WILD. Joe is not really in the know about Elon Musk buying Twitter, but he is down with wearing women's underwear!The boys talk about shit going down on planes lately - no masks, Mike Tyson punching other passengers, and mile high club? You decide if it was..... Mike Tyson can't fight Joe list though, he trains as a MMA and Jiu Jitsu fighter, DON'T MESS WITH JOE!-- check it out! Boys close it out with Joe giving Chris some advice on how to do Joe Rogan's podcast. WHAT SHOULD CHRIS TALK ABOUT WITH JOE ROGAN!? 
 
Remember to rate us on iTunes and Join our Patreon for a WEEKLY bonus ep!
